      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Inland Empire Railway Co.\nhas ordered 1000 tons of rails for\nextensions from Palouse to Moscow\nplanned for this year. The rails\nare steel, weighing from 60 to 70\npounds, and are TO be delivered in\nthe spring and early summer. The\norder was placed with the Carnegie\nmills at Pittsburg."
    }
